          <li><a href="/goddess-yoga-retreats">Goddess Yoga Retreats</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-col">
        <h4>CONTACT</h4>
        <p>For collaborations, readings, or mystical inquiries — send a raven... or just an email.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="footer-cta">send a message</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-quote">
      <p>"A sacred space for divine insight and mystical connection."</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer-bottom">
      <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Tarot Flower &middot; All Rights Reserved &middot; <a href="/terms-and-conditions">Privacy Policy</a> &middot; Site by Vanessa Hylande</p>
